Ghosts vs. Monsters is a physics-based game template designed for mobile devices.  It was created by Jonathan Beebe and Biffy Beebe for Corona SDK, made by Ansca Mobile, http://www.anscamobile.com. It's designed for game creators who want to make games like Angry Birds for iPhone, iPad, and Android devices.  Jonathan and Biffy created this game in 36 hours.  Download the files and start creating your own physics game.